        "text_pxNH7J": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Sunny yellows and harmonious blues, inspired by the enduring appeal of blue and white Indian textiles and ceramics - a timeless combination that feels endlessly fresh for summer.</p><p>The colour palette for Peony Urn pastel takes its cue from soft, sun-washed shades of pistachio, lemon, strawberry and cream. Gentle tones inspired by Italian gelato and the weathered elegance of grand Italian villas. </p><p>Romantic and relaxed, these colours sit beautifully alongside classic British garden hues, creating tablescapes that feel both refined and inviting.</p>",
            "code": ""
          }
        },
